    <item>
      <title>Variáveis e tipos de dados</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/disciplinas/apc-1/variaveis-tipos-de-dados/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/disciplinas/apc-1/variaveis-tipos-de-dados/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;Em Python, uma variável é utilizada para armazenar valores na memória. Esses valores podem ser utilizados, modificados e reutilizados ao longo do programa.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Variáveis&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;variáveis&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#vari%c3%a1veis&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Para criar uma variável, basta atribuir um valor utilizando o operador &lt;code&gt;=&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;x &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;nome &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Ana&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Neste caso, &lt;code&gt;x&lt;/code&gt; armazena um número e &lt;code&gt;nome&lt;/code&gt; armazena um texto.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;O nome da variável deve seguir algumas regras:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Não pode começar com número&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Não pode conter espaços&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deve evitar palavras reservadas da linguagem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Tipagem dinâmica&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;tipagem-dinâmica&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#tipagem-din%c3%a2mica&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Python é uma linguagem de tipagem dinâmica. Isso significa que não é necessário declarar o tipo da variável, pois ele é definido automaticamente.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;x &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span style=&#34;color:#57606a&#34;&gt;# inteiro&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;x &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;texto&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#57606a&#34;&gt;# agora é uma string&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A variável pode mudar de tipo ao longo do programa.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Tipos básicos de dados&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;tipos-básicos-de-dados&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#tipos-b%c3%a1sicos-de-dados&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Inteiros (int)&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;inteiros-int&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#inteiros-int&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Representam números inteiros.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;idade &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Números reais (float)&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;números-reais-float&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#n%c3%bameros-reais-float&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Representam números com casas decimais.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;altura &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;1.75&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Texto (str)&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;texto-str&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#texto-str&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Representa sequências de caracteres.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;nome &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;João&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;mensagem &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;Olá mundo&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Booleano (bool)&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;booleano-bool&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#booleano-bool&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Representa valores lógicos: verdadeiro ou falso.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;ativo &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#cf222e&#34;&gt;True&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;aprovado &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#cf222e&#34;&gt;False&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Verificando o tipo&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;verificando-o-tipo&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#verificando-o-tipo&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;A função &lt;code&gt;type()&lt;/code&gt; permite verificar o tipo de uma variável.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;x &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6639ba&#34;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6639ba&#34;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Conversão de tipos&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;conversão-de-tipos&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#convers%c3%a3o-de-tipos&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;É possível converter valores entre diferentes tipos de dados.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;x &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;10&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;y &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6639ba&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
